bilingual.source: Today, satellite data and computer technology help scientists predict the weather more precisely.
bilingual.target: 如今，卫星数据和计算机技术帮助科学家更精确地预测天气。

bilingual.source: The clock is set precisely to the atomic time.
bilingual.target: 这时钟精确地设置为原子时间。

bilingual.source: He can recall the events of that day precisely.
bilingual.target: 他能精确地回忆起那天的事件。

bilingual.source: You can tune your engine more precisely with a dyno.
bilingual.target: 你可以用动力测试仪更精确地调校发动机。

bilingual.source: She measured the ingredients precisely for the recipe.
bilingual.target: 她精确地测量了食谱中的配料。

bilingual.source: The executor needs to follow the instructions precisely.
bilingual.target: 执行者需要精确地遵循指示。

bilingual.source: The lab technician measured out the mercaptoethanol precisely.
bilingual.target: 实验室技术员精确地量取了巯基乙醇。

bilingual.source: CNC technology can precisely control the movement of machines.
bilingual.target: 数控技术可以精确地控制机器的运动。

bilingual.source: The interferometer measures the wavelength of light very precisely.
bilingual.target: 干涉仪非常精确地测量光的波长。

yingyinNormal.en: So we'd be perpetrating a ruse? Precisely.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这么说我们是要做戏咯？一点没错。

yingyinNormal.en: What time is checkout? In precisely one hour.
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么时候退房？还有一个小时。

yingyinNormal.en: This is so precisely not the way to win me over!
yingyinNormal.zh: 这绝不是赢得我心的办法！

yingyinNormal.en: Precisely. North Yorkshire has a lot of these estates, big and small.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没错。北约克郡有很多这样的庄园，大小都有。

yingyinNormal.en: The world is an infinitely better place precisely because you weren't.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因为你的不平凡，世界才变得更加美好。

yingyinNormal.en: Precisely. But don't fear. I'll call on Miss Cruikshank before I leave.
yingyinNormal.zh: 正是，不过别担心，我会先见见克鲁克山小姐再走。

yingyinNormal.en: Precisely, I didn't do anything. Now does someone feel like checking her emotional math?
yingyinNormal.zh: 对啊，我什么都没干啊，某人是不是该仔细想想自己在说啥啊？

yingyinNormal.en: More precisely, we used your loofah. I exfoliated her brains out. You can keep that, too.
yingyinNormal.zh: 准确地说，是我俩用了，我把她搓得欲仙欲死。这个也送给你了。

yingyinNormal.en: So he gives himself the idea. Precisely. That's the only way it will stick. It has to seem self-generated.
yingyinNormal.zh: 总言之他自己为自己植入意念。没错，让他自然而然有此意念。

yingyinNormal.en: M's idea? Precisely. Oh, one word of warning. The alarm is rather loud. If you know what I mean. I think I do.
yingyinNormal.zh: M的主意吗？正是，要提醒你下，闹钟声音挺响的，你要是懂我意思的话。明白。

yingyinNormal.en: Typical. Tea. We did not communicate through mere words. Our souls met. Precisely. My soul and the prince's soul.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真独特。茶。我们不需用言语交流，我们的灵魂相遇了。准确的说，我的灵魂和王子的灵魂。

yingyinNormal.en: And I'm having trouble precisely evaluating the time of my death but I doubt I'll last more than twenty-four hours.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我无法准确预测自己的死期，但我认为应该不会超过一天。

yingyinNormal.en: They saw this polarization pattern that was precisely what was predicted except that it was stronger than expected.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但他们看到了这个极化形状，正是所预测的除了它比预测的更强。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes, I'm trying to figure out the nanometer and the attosecond, precisely where and when an event of awareness takes place.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是的，我在试着得出何处与何时意识在大脑中产生，精确到纳米与原子秒。

yingyinNormal.en: Music and light bringing dreams to life? Precisely. Well, it's just like you remember it. In fact, I've made it even more spectacular.
yingyinNormal.zh: 音乐和灯光将梦想带入现实，美仑美央。剧院现在还是风采依旧。而且，我把它打造得更棒了。

yingyinNormal.en: In addition to all his other crops, he's an expert at producing Blooming Onions, 1,500 tons of them every year, precisely to his customer's specifications.
yingyinNormal.zh: 除了他种植的其他作物，他还是一位制作开花洋葱的专家，每年生产1500吨，完全按照消费者需求来生产的洋葱。

yingyinNormal.en: And next. If either of us ever invents time travel, we agree our first stop will be this meeting today in precisely five seconds. Okay. That's disappointing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 下一条，如果我们之中任何一人发明了时空穿梭机，我们同意第一站就是回到今天这个会议，时间是5秒之后。好。真可惜。
